Package com.bakdata.dedupe.similarity

Class CommonTransformations

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.bakdata.dedupe.similarity.CommonTransformations
  • public final class CommonTransformations
extends java.lang.Object
    A utility class that offers factory methods for common similarity transformations. Usually, these methods are included through static imports.

    For new transformations, please open an issue or PR on Github }.

    See Also:
    CommonSimilarityMeasures
